# JackSparrow Project Documentation Context

The `.cursor/context/docs` directory mirrors the entire `docs/` tree. Reference this file when you need to know which documentation files are available. Load specific documentation files on-demand using `@` mentions or explicit file references:

**To load documentation context:**
- Use `@.cursor/context/docs/<filename>` to reference specific docs
- Use `@Folders .cursor/context/docs` to load all docs (use sparingly)
- Reference individual files directly when needed

